<br /><br />&quot;How much do you charge?&quot;
<br /><br />&quot;Eighty dollars per visit, replied the doctor.&quot;
<br /><br />&quot;I'll sleep on it,&quot; said Bubba.
<br /><br />Six months later the doctor met Bubba on the street. &quot;Why didn't you ever come to see me about those fears you were having?&quot; asked the psychiatrist.
<br /><br />&quot;Well Eighty bucks a visit three times a week for a year is an awful lot of money! A bartender cured me for $10.00 I was so happy to have saved all that money that I went and bought me a new pickup!&quot;
